songs.title: To who you want
songs.lyrics:
[Snippet:]
I probably won't be back in a long time (Consider that)
I hate the way we talk like I'm your fuckin' hotline (Line)
When I talk to you, you givin' me all chills (Chills)
'Cause when I don't love you, baby, give it to who you want

This is a rumored song, may be a hoax, may be true
Details are unknown at the moment
